item.title: FsCheck and co: Testing Excel Financial Functions
item.description: Excel Financial Functions library is a .NET library written by Luca Bolognese that provides the full set of financial functions from Excel. It can be used from both F# and C# as well as from other .NET languages. The main goal for the library is compatibility with Excel, by providing the same functions, with the same behaviour. The library was recently moved to GitHub and its new home is here.
